      "time_str": "00:53.330",
      "text": "八厘米纪录片的桥段",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 55.88,
      "time_str": "00:55.880",
      "text": "隔着距离欣赏",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 57.93,
      "time_str": "00:57.930",
      "text": "正邪对立的两方我握紧拳头",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
